function App() { const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState(''); const [selectedCategory, setSelectedCategory] = useState('전체'); const [filteredBrands, setFilteredBrands] = useState(brandsData); useEffect(() => { let filtered = brandsData; if (selectedCategory !== '전체') { filtered = filtered.filter(brand => brand.category === selectedCategory); } if (searchTerm) { filtered = filtered.filter(brand => brand.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) || brand.nameKr.includes(searchTerm) || brand.country.includes(searchTerm) ); } setFilteredBrands(filtered); }, [searchTerm, selectedCategory]); return (
